These are the minutes for the September 11th, 2014 SPI Board Meeting,
held at 20:00 UTC in #spi on irc.spi-inc.org.
[LOG](../../../logs/2014/2014-09-11-log.txt).


## President's Report

Bdale Garbee was not present, so there is no report from the President.


## Treasurer's report

Michael Schultheiss was not present, so there is no report from the
Treasurer.


## Secretary's report

Martin Michlmayr stated that the web site and by-laws had been updated to
reflect the current directors and officers.  Martin Zobel-Helas kindly
prepared minutes for the August meeting.  Martin Michlmayr found a minor
inaccuracy in the July minutes which he proposed to fix without
re-approval from the board; there were no objections.


